{
  "stem": "2684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They took us to factories, which I can't remember name, where we have to-- had to clean up the, the rubbles and, and sweep and, and, and try to-- we didn't have the right to interfere with the-- with either the Red Cross or, or the ambulance services or the fire brigade.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But after everybody left, we cleaned up whatever rubble that is left after bombardment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And when, when they didn't needed us, we went out again, to do the roads.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And one day, a truck came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We thought we're going home early.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But the truck was loaded with-- oh, I could say around ten Gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The Gendarmes were a special Hungarian force which had a feather on their hat, and they were very feared by Jews because they were a very, very anti-Semitic organization.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They were the policeman in the country, not in the capital city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Budapest had a police force.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "The, the country had these Gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And they came, not the police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And all they did, they put us onto the trucks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And from Nagyteteny, they took us into Budateteny into a school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Budateteny was just a next little village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And into the school came one of these Gendarmes who was, according to my estimation, a lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And the rest of them was just the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And in the school, strange things happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "He started interrogate us one by one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And when the guys came out from the interrogation room, they looked a little bit untidy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And as a youngster, I didn't have any knowledge what's going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "When I got in, then I realized actually what's happening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "He called me to the desk he was sitting, and he moved his chair, sitting position, and asked me to come close.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
